# ai-cli

Offline AI assistant for code writing, command execution, and chat working with any offline models.

## Installation

```bash
pip install ai-cli
```

## Usage

```bash
ai-cli --help
```

## Features

- Code generation and assistance
- Command execution
- Chat interface
- Works with any offline models (Ollama, llama.cpp, etc.)
